data.description: **HUGE PRICE REDUCTION!! Spacious 2-story home. 1st floor remodeled and 2nd floor addition in 2002. The home boasts a free-standing gas fireplace and large bedrooms with walk-in closets. Plenty of storage area with shop & attic storage. The property features RV parking and is zoned for 1 large animal, making it ideal for those who love outdoor activities. Mature blackberry & grape vines. The heated 36ft x 22ft shop provides ample space for a workshop or storage. Close to several schools & park. Additionally, the property is conveniently located near the FrontRunner and shopping.  All information provided as a courtesy. Buyer to verify.
